
Special thanks to Sydesy who sponsored this development

Installation
------------

1. Copy the entire civicrm_taxonomy_sync folder into your modules directory .

2. Log in to your site as an administrator, and go to the Administer >> Site building >> Modules
   section. Enable  the civicrm_forum_sync module.
   


  

Configuration
-------------

1. Goto admin/settings/civicrm-taxonomy-sync and import the forums tagging structure. Enjoy 
